// Header
// Desktop application header. Contains project selector, session selector,
// theme toggle, edit mode, chat toggle, terminal toggle, and session management
// actions (create, delete, refresh). Also handles todo navigation.

projects: derived from sessions + registeredProjects, deduped and sorted.
projectSessions: sessions for the selected project, excluding todo-linked sessions.
Syncs selectedProject with currentSession.project. Auto-selects first project
if none is set.
Dropdowns close on outside click or Escape.

FUNCTION Header(onSessionSelect, onCreateSession, onDeleteSession) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Reads session list, selected project, and collab state from stores.
  Renders: project dropdown, session dropdown, connection status dot,
  phase badge, todos button, theme/edit/chat/terminal icon buttons, refresh.

---

FUNCTION getProjectDisplayName(path) -> string
  Returns the basename (last path segment) of the project path.

---

FUNCTION handleProjectSelect(project) -> void
  Sets selectedProject. Auto-selects the first session in the project, or
  clears currentSession if the project has no sessions.

---

FUNCTION handleSessionClick(session) -> void
  Calls onSessionSelect(session). Closes session dropdown.

---

FUNCTION handleThemeToggle() -> void
  Toggles light/dark theme in uiStore.

---

FUNCTION handleEditModeToggle() -> void
  Toggles diagram edit mode in uiStore.

---

FUNCTION handleChatToggle() -> void
  Toggles the chat panel visibility.

---

FUNCTION handleTerminalToggle() -> void
  Toggles the terminal panel visibility.

---

FUNCTION handleRefreshSessions() -> void
  Calls api.getSessions to reload the sessions list.

---

FUNCTION handleAddProject() -> void
  Prompts for a project path and calls api.registerProject if non-empty.

---

FUNCTION handleRemoveProject(project) -> void
  Confirms with the user then calls api.unregisterProject.

---

FUNCTION handleCreateSession() -> void
  Calls onCreateSession for the selectedProject.

---

FUNCTION handleTodosClick() -> void
  Calls selectTodos + api.getTodos for selectedProject.

---

FUNCTION handleDeleteSession(session, e) -> void
  Stops event propagation. Calls onDeleteSession(session).
